@startuml ComponentCustomExtensions
title METRIC - Extensões Customizadas (RF002)
package "Plugin Host" {
    component [Extension API] as ExtAPI
    interface "IDataSourcePlugin" as IDS
    interface "IActivityPlugin" as IAct
}

package "Custom Extensions" {
    [ERP Adapter] --> IDS
    [Custom Timer Logic] --> IAct
    [Webhook Listener] --> IAct
}

ExtAPI -- IDS
ExtAPI -- IAct
note right of ExtAPI
  Plugins customizados
  para integração com
  outros Data Sources
end note
@enduml
